The United States strongly condemns the terrorist attack in Jerusalem that resulted in the death of four Israeli soldiers and injuries to many others. The US offers its full support to Israel as they investigate and determine those responsible for the attack. Such acts of terrorism are unjustifiable and should never be tolerated. The US calls on everyone to send a clear message that terrorism is unacceptable. Condolences are extended to the families of the victims, and hopes for a speedy recovery are expressed for those wounded.